{"tid":2300743,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"IT狗係咪死路一條...","createTime":"2020-11-25T18:30:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T18:05:32.000Z","uid":65276,"like":24,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"3fb9d2b5a355c9d8add1faadc7c7b8a21c20d881","tid":2300743,"uid":65276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T18:30:37.000Z","msg":"今日4:00pm係公園見到個乞衣,而我就用緊手提電腦寫緊個程式.....<br />\n<br />\n程式行極都錯, 要fix bugs. 但我唔知邊到錯...<br />\n<br />\n個乞衣突然行過黎坐左係我身邊<br />\n<br />\n見佢咁慘, 我就打算俾$100 打發佢走<br />\n<br />\n佢雙手收左我$100蚊, 面露笑容, 準備離開...<br />\n<br />\n就係佢準備離開既時候..<br />\n<br />\n個乞衣緩緩地指著我notebook個screen..<br />\n<br />\n講左一句，這裡少了個分號.........<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPS. 個乞衣大約40歲, 而我就28歲做緊IT."},{"pid":"8b3fef93260afb0756699d8872017bff3ab0cd5e","tid":2300743,"uid":236505,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T18:52:35.000Z","msg":"其實個乞兒係未來返左黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"177262f9a159ff20cd7d2eba40cfbae3d762603a","tid":2300743,"uid":81113,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T18:54:00.000Z","msg":"咪膠啦⋯⋯少個分號早就出咗exception話你知啦"},{"pid":"00892347213fb550ebb1db6500bb81b9956cd897","tid":2300743,"uid":134522,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T19:28:35.000Z","msg":"syntax error compiler會話你知架"},{"pid":"6558af46ccd0223a2e6678441ae3945cf6037f21","tid":2300743,"uid":2054,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T19:42:55.000Z","msg":"個乞衣緩緩地指著我notebook個screen..<br />\n<br />\n講左一句，這裡少了句是咁的........."},{"pid":"7ac8b4b3f87e80973edd438e8c8024940f5b2c5b","tid":2300743,"uid":268516,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T20:23:38.000Z","msg":"戴住口罩 你點見到佢面露笑容<br />\n重作啦"},{"pid":"3d6d5ec7beab36d05b2ea19da6d5ceedf86ddb3e","tid":2300743,"uid":211935,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T20:27:37.000Z","msg":"你俾得$100乞衣都唔窮得去邊啦"},{"pid":"0f2c86a7a3b